"optional argument can be specified with an `=` symbol. This argument is only "
"appended to the `--enable-_entry_` configure option. For example:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Table
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/makefiles/chapter.adoc:3828
msgid ""
"....  OPTIONS_DEFINE=\tOPT1 OPT2 OPT1_CONFIGURE_ENABLE=\ttest1 test2 "
"OPT2_CONFIGURE_ENABLE=\ttest2=exhaustive ....  is equivalent to:"
